item.title: Introduction to Urban Institute Education Data API
item.description: The Urban Institute released a public API that pulls and pre-processes data from various sources of education institution data, including but not limited to the Department of Education. We used their R package to explore the relationship between applicant and enrollment volume. To install the R, you must have the devtools library installed…
